title: Coral skeletons left by major earthquake over 630 years ago serve as a warning for Caribbean region
description: An catastrophic earthquake rocked the north eastern Caribbean sometime between 1381 and 1391.
content:
Coral skeletons left by a tsunami over 630 years ago are a warning for the Caribbean region, according to new research.
An earthquake exceeding magnitude 8.0 rocked the north eastern Caribbean somet… [+3804 chars]
de: Korallenskelette, die ein schweres Erdbeben vor über 630 Jahren hinterlassen hat, dienen als Warnung für die Karibikregion. Irgendwann zwischen 1381 und 1391 erschütterte ein katastrophales Erdbeben die Nordostkaribik.
en: Coral skeletons left by major earthquake over 630 years ago serve as a warning for Caribbean region. An catastrophic earthquake rocked the north eastern Caribbean sometime between 1381 and 1391.
la: Sceleta corallia maioribus terrae motu super 630 annos relicta sunt ut admonitio regionis Caribbeae sit. Terrae motus calamitosus movebatur ad septentrionem orientalem Caribbean olim inter 1381 et 1391 .

title: Earthquakes strike Indonesia, Philippines, no tsunami threat to Malaysia
description: KUALA LUMPUR: Two moderate earthquakes were recorded in Indonesia and the Philippines on Thursday (Jan 1) morning. Read full story

de: Erdbeben erschüttern Indonesien und die Philippinen, für Malaysia besteht keine Tsunami-Gefahr. KUALA LUMPUR: Am Donnerstagmorgen (1. Januar) wurden in Indonesien und auf den Philippinen zwei mittelschwere Erdbeben registriert. Lesen Sie die ganze Geschichte
